{"tid":2084622,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年 作為樓淡應該如何自處","createTime":"2020-06-29T10:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T14:03:40.000Z","uid":59546,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2817013b8f868cf8250302d7fb9c8a2b3a57935c","tid":2084622,"uid":59546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"我地樓淡現實已經冇可能搵到d有樓睇淡既人 最近上連登終於有個巴打h<span style=\"color: red;\">a</span>h<span style=\"color: red;\">a</span>000有樓睇淡支援下啦 點知講講下完來自己strong hold 明睇淡實睇好 同以前中學嗰d我冇溫書 結果考試第一嗰d 冇分別咁都算 而家仲潛埋水 <br />\n<br />\n現實冇樓睇淡更加唔好講 一開口吹淡就見到d私樓朋友笑而不語個樣 真係講多兩講自己都尷尷尬尬😅 唯一途徑就上連燈發下up風 結果班樓好又追住我地嚟咬 最慘係咩呢 班樓好都冇吹好 冇講過咩樓價升幾多 講埋哂d橫行都跑贏我地買股 相反我地樓淡日日吹跌 死人樓市跌一星期就反升10星期 仲有d領軍人物失雞無神就自貼credit limit然後潛水<br />\n<br />\n究竟幾時先到我地出頭天 雖然跌一半我地都係買唔起 但可摸耳比我地贏返一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8a8fd912431f432665f1d2cb766dcd9106c0c9","tid":2084622,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"要冇晒淡淡先真係會跌架<br />\n個個都睇淡跌條撚咩"},{"pid":"a727d2047733ff5e90437d730c2b660d754e62ff","tid":2084622,"uid":57671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T10:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pWsavmb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpWsavmb.jpg&h=cd1318a2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JOMZoGd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJOMZoGd.jpg&h=a6ae71e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1GZoGe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1GZoGe.jpg&h=0d4591f3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z00joGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz00joGf.jpg&h=4056509e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yv6Og1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYv6Og1f.jpg&h=64a33f35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i